description:
The Dragon Princess, Knitted Uniform & Land Mine Girl Skin Bundle includes:
- Dragon Princess costume
- Knitted Uniform costume
- Land Mine Girl costume

There are no unlock conditions for these costumes. They will become available in-game upon purchase.

*The Dragon Princess, Knitted Uniform, and Land Mine Girl costumes are all purely cosmetic.
name: Dragon Princess, Knitted Uniform & Land Mine Girl Skin Bundle
